name: Historical landings from the Trieste (Italy) fish market between 1902 and 1968
description: Historical landings from the Trieste (currentlyItaly) fish marketfor the period 1902-1968(with some temporal gaps) were retrieved and entered in a digitalformat from the official statisticalbulletin (paper format) of the Municipality of Trieste. At that time, Trieste fish marketwas one of the most important in the areatogether with Rijeka (currently Croatia) and Venice(Italy).
